{"tid":1646491,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"重申：香港示威「五大綱領」","createTime":"2019-10-11T10:16:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-11T15:36:41.000Z","uid":73915,"like":93,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"8fafd37360a2afc63d56810952fdccc4754c3f08","tid":1646491,"uid":73915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T10:16:01.000Z","msg":"五大綱領，並非教條<br />\n<br />\n1。不割蓆<br />\n「d人破壞店鋪好暴力，我唔贊成」❌<br />\n「不如等我了解下點解你會裝修黨鐵吖？」✅<br />\n<br />\n2。不指責<br />\n「你日日開花，破壞晒民權法進程喇」❌<br />\n「你唱歌搞到成個運動膠化晒喇」❌<br />\n「開花同唱歌，都係想打擊政權同爪牙姐」✅<br />\n<br />\n3。不分化<br />\n「今日和理非回合、勇武退場」❌<br />\n「今日18區裝修，唔夠勇就唔好出」❌<br />\n「不如放低個豬嘴，一齊唱歌吖」✅<br />\n「比d防護裝備你，幫手傳下物資，派下食物吖」✅<br />\n<br />\n4。不談判<br />\n「林鄭對話會，傾下好過唔傾吖」❌<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」✅<br />\n<br />\n5。各有各做，兄弟爬山，各自努力<br />\n「遊行廢既，唔好搞啦，政府唔會理你地」❌<br />\n「唔好用暴力，打交只會破壞民意」❌<br />\n「今日港島遊行，九龍新界開花，完左一齊食宵夜吖」✅"},{"pid":"4f465eff717330deb62781c3c1b7417b864e0a75","tid":1646491,"uid":55271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T10:17:23.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68b9d60d75ec4dee3eb4eb2f263e9a0976696bae","tid":1646491,"uid":73915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T10:18:46.000Z","msg":"自推1/10"},{"pid":"7799ffcff7bfc3aa9584e1ab342bec507bea3b99","tid":1646491,"uid":199257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T10:19:08.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"3516fdb4dd4a29794a4b69918bf60eed3d90924b","tid":1646491,"uid":55271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T10:19:22.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"fd319953ed1dfd7ec94c4ce7fc403d5146ce85ac","tid":1646491,"uid":82253,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T10:19:49.000Z","msg":"真心，唔好捉鬼同俾人分化<br />\n另外<br />\n各自努力有新方向，就係打籃球<br />\n<br />\n籃球活動：1025-26#StandWithMorey榮光盃<br />\n<a href=\"ht